Package: statclinix
Type: Package
Title: Streamlined Statistical Summaries and Visualizations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Tuhin", "Rana", 
                  email = "rana2hin@gmail.com", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-6401-8326"))
Description: A collection of user-friendly functions to generate 
    publication-ready tables and plots, primarily for clinical 
    research. Simplifies the creation of summary tables, correlation 
    plots, and various customized charts using 'ggplot2' and 'gtsummary'.
